## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification
1.  **Check GAS Executions**:
    - Go to [script.google.com](https://script.google.com) > Open your project.
    - Click **"Execuções"** (Executions) on the left sidebar.
    - Check if any requests are listed and if they finished with "Completed" or "Failed".
2.  **Redeploy the Script**:
    - Click **"Implantar"** (Deploy) > **"Gerenciar Implantações"** (Manage Deployments).
    - Edit the existing deployment and select **"Nova Versão"** (New Version).
    - Ensure access is still set to "Anyone".
3.  **Test the Form**:
    - Fill out the form and submit.
